{"tid":1940710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［要人］法國共諜學棍Jon Solomon 聯署叫人搞鳩袁國勇 中大生反擊 聯署要求法國大調查","createTime":"2020-03-24T02:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T03:06:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab123f745a98a65a2bdc16679c610ce716dfbd63","tid":1940710,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇及名譽助理教授龍振邦，日前於明報以《大流行緣起武漢 十七年教訓盡忘》撰文，其後撤回。法國尚慕蘭里昂第三大學學者蘇哲安(Jon Solomon)認為文章構成「殖民種族歧視(colonial racism)」，於網上發起聯署要求校方調查袁國勇及重新考慮其聘任等。惟蘇哲安昨再發起聯署，指《明報》報道藏頭露尾，「有刻意隱瞞事實、扭曲事實、抹黑本人之嫌」，要求《明報》更正⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n另外，有中大學生今就事件發起聯署，指蘇哲安的言論誤導，更要求就一個科學家的言論作出處分。而在親北京人士積推動 23 條立法、港人擔憂言論自由受損之際，無論他是否有意為之，做法都涉打壓異見，並認為聯署並不專業科學，助長北京對港的白色恐怖。聯署又要求法國尚慕蘭里昂第三大學就事件展開調查，及重新考慮對蘇哲安的聘任。聯署至今有逾 150 人參與。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/撤文風波-聯署指袁國勇-龍振邦文章涉殖民種族歧視-法國學者再聯署指-明報-扭曲事實-抹黑/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%92%A4%E6%96%87%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87-%E9%BE%8D%E6%8C%AF%E9%82%A6%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%B6%89%E6%AE%96%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E5%86%8D%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87-%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%B1-%E6%89%AD%E6%9B%B2%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6-%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%2F&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1pgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=040e8305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%92%A4%E6%96%87%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87-%E9%BE%8D%E6%8C%AF%E9%82%A6%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%B6%89%E6%AE%96%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E5%86%8D%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87-%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%B1-%E6%89%AD%E6%9B%B2%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6-%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%2F&h=1bea1ea3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/撤文風波-聯署指袁國勇-龍振邦文章涉殖民種族歧視-法國學者再聯署指-明報-扭曲事實-抹黑/</a><br />\n<br />\n中大聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/president-s-office-of-lyon-iii-university-call-for-academic-justice-to-hong-kong-and-condemn-jon-solomon?recruiter=1059760002&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition&amp;fbclid=IwAR2QbNOEvDzPjMpfgRymSmRoc1zTilNjsG2xGJxL3OhVD6Tri-pOPI7PH4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fpresident-s-office-of-lyon-iii-university-call-for-academic-justice-to-hong-kong-and-condemn-jon-solomon%3Frecruiter%3D1059760002%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dshare_petition%26fbclid%3DIwAR2QbNOEvDzPjMpfgRymSmRoc1zTilNjsG2xGJxL3OhVD6Tri-pOPI7PH4Y&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1pgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=69e1640c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/president-s-office-of-lyon-iii-university-call-for-academic-justice-to-hong-kong-and-condemn-jon-solomon?recruiter=1059760002&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition&amp;fbclid=IwAR2QbNOEvDzPjMpfgRymSmRoc1zTilNjsG2xGJxL3OhVD6Tri-pOPI7PH4Y</a>"},{"pid":"c51b180ed471d454aa7b5ce6c7a96ee02744939f","tid":1940710,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"條友之前出咗篇1999論文暗插反送中運動（見英文標題）<br />\n<br />\n香港，社會鬥爭與資本主義圈地運動<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong, or How Social Struggles Can Reinforce the Cartography of Capitalist Enclosure<br />\n<br />\nBy Jon Solomon<br />\n<br />\n本文作者蘇哲安（Jon Solomon）現為法國里昂第三大學中文系教授，曾於台灣與香港研究與教書，批判香港反對「《逃犯條例》修正草案」運動如何繼承了殖民－帝國現代性的問題，並指出其如何再次強化主權的劃界，在此之下，所謂「自由」下所隱含的一種本質上具有人種優越感（speciestic）的未來想像，悖反地又將自身「封鎖進資本主義社會關係的再生產所必需的那些圈封的國家或區域，遭受前所未有的奴役」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://jonsolomon.academia.edu/research#papers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjonsolomon.academia.edu%2Fresearch%23papers&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1pgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=62befe37\" target=\"_blank\">https://jonsolomon.academia.edu/research#papers</a>"},{"pid":"813062a3c675c65ef062d83e339d53f77b52faeb","tid":1940710,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"條友又係cornell出身<br />\nCornell出過好多共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見<br />\n[所謂專家] 中美貿易戰論輸贏 權威證據：美國才是輸家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1047886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1047886</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9e2fce8951732336df82c79c5e6bdd3aa21e4ff0","tid":1940710,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:57:01.000Z","msg":"共諜都唔好做得咁明顯吖大佬<br />\n小心工都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81f1f723010ed3ec2b2d8cb6ff592596e09501f","tid":1940710,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"推、簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b58ff04666f889c3ce81d1bff3eefbf6b65363","tid":1940710,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T02:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b3215a15520ab59011a2396be4a5567d711178","tid":1940710,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96465617b65c3107247d49f63835ec9872614fa9","tid":1940710,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"馬卡龍自己都係共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d80fa3ddefd2744d7bbedcef8992178af4c35d8","tid":1940710,"uid":4808